Print forester models

Source: R/print.R
print.forester.Rd

The generic `print()` function creates and prints numeric sumamry of forester models.

# S3 method for forester
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

a model created with the `train()` function

...

other parameters

Value

side effect - prints something on the screen
